    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "Gentlemen:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "Further to my previous letters, I am attaching a photostat of some",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "recent correspondence with a new subscriber, MR. [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "president of [REDACTED] From some of the facts mentioned",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "in his letter, I think he may be a part of the possibly subversive group",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "that I have previously mentioned.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "I find it very difficult to believe any ordinary person would spend",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "depending on type of coverage, from $250. to $1200. per year, for 6 years",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "on clipping services, on a subject for whatever \"pleasure I am able to get",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "out of it.\" And after this, remain \"somewhat nebulous\" on the matter. I",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "would suggest a check of files on this name as well as others previously",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "mentioned.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "His appearance within 2 weeks after mentioning to [REDACTED] that",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "it would require several thousand dollars, is also a little too well timed.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "She has also stated that the 6 person business meetings, held in her home",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "between public meetings is not too necessary, and that I only need appear.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "She has spoken to Mr. [REDACTED] several times, and mentioned that he may be",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "able to appear at one of these business meetings, and planned for next month.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "From this, I would assume that they either plan further attempts to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "obtain information from me, or make a possible business agreement to further",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "work. I do not plan to enter any agreement, in the possibility it is only",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "INDEXED 162-10425",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "If you require any further information, my files are at your disposal.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "All above material is once again, from implications I gather of the persons",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "mentioned, and I do not have any concrete data to back these suspicions, or",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "have no accusations to make.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
